Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I only believe in the future, I don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,it's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I follow, follow in the footsteps of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,of a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go with you, so passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I don't really need everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...? What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.11,0:01:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! There's a flock of birds to starboard!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.24,0:02:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.45,0:02:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.41,0:02:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...Grab!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec... Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.71,0:02:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.26,0:02:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A wind is coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A strong wind is...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like this ship hasn't been moving at all for a while...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.29,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...! \NWe've entered the Calm Belt!!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.25,0:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Charm Belt?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.54,0:02:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm Belt! It's an area of sea \Nwhere nothing moves a muscle!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nami grew her muscles"?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.72,0:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake? On the sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, enough chit chat!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fold the sails and start paddling now!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the ship back on its earlier path!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.62,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.74,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you panicking about? \NPaddling? This is a sailboat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. \NWhy're we taking the trouble to go back
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to where the Navy is waiting for us?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.28,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what I say! \NWe're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the sea is quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.25,0:03:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fine! \NThen I'll explain it for you! Listen up!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.17,0:03:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we rushed and ran away, \Nwe came further south than we planned!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.17,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then did we enter the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.01,0:03:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was that easy, anyone could enter!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.43,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. The Grand Line is running between two sea areas!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.11,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The area on both sides of \Nit is called the Calm Belt.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.28,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is unknown but in these areas, \Nthere's no wind and no current.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're an area of sea with complete calm.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sailboats run by catching winds, \Nso it's an extremely dangerous area,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,indeed, a fatal area, for them!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, did you get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At least that we're in trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Good, you got more than I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what the geezer meant \Nwhen he said it was dangerous...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder there hasn't been any wind.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything if the ship doesn't move.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just wait until the wind starts blowing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, once you're in \Nthis area, wind never blows
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how long you wait! \NAnd, that's not all!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.14,0:04:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another reason that \Npeople call this area dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In this area...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Another one!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is coming this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are!!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're huge!!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calm Belt is the nest of the Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.31,0:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the ones here are super huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.19,0:05:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're another reason why \Npeople can't cross the Calm Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:32.29,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,108)}Miraculous Creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:32.29,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,458)\fs55}Apis's Secret and \Nthe Legendary Island
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,F-For the time being, no one move.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll probably go back into the sea eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.29,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll paddle hard using our oars.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.34,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A frog is coming!!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What?! What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.60,0:06:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your arm is stretching!!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! \NDo you have the power of a devil fruit?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stretch your arm downwards again!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.81,0:06:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she just do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She pulled his nose hair.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.53,0:06:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec...!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.66,0:07:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna sneeze!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a huge nose hair!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We're going back!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it some other way!!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.64,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! I feel like we're flying!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.68,0:07:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}are{\i0} flying!!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're back in the area we came from.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any sign of the Navy, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.87,0:07:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... I thought I was a goner.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Unfurl the sails!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our destination is...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Warship Island!!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't see anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can see the fog.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis, is it really around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.84,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Not sure"? You...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.64,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be close by.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure know your stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...! Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.27,0:08:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.19,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's a sailboat! It's huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen here...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.70,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The word "huge" doesn't begin to describe it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, a super humongous sailboat?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Warship Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shaped like a warship, \Nso it's called Warship Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That flag is...!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates!! Pirates have come!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.60,0:08:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay inside!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! I'm home!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis...!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you coming out from the pirate ship?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a BBQ restaurant on this island?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.81,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! \NThey're pirates, but they're good ones.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there really good pirates?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.24,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you taken away by \Nthe Navy in the first place?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. But I escaped.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.29,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And these guys, Luffy and \Nthe others, saved me. Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do, Apis?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.29,0:09:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know why, but the \NNavy was looking for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay away from your home.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still around.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.47,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to help, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're pirates, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, what should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Like she said, we're good pirates.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my house!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.20,0:10:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Bokuden!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving Apis.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.75,0:10:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this? I'd like to throw \Na small welcome party for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.43,0:10:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your place a BBQ restaurant?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a BBQ restaurant,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.85,0:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but Grandpa Bokuden's pork buns \Nare the best on the island!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.85,0:10:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll go.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.41,0:11:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eric!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been here all along...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that that girl got lost in the Calm Belt
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and wasn't going to come back alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.26,0:11:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be... That girl...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.28,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...back on Warship Island! \NCapture that girl, you bum!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.78,0:11:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they escaped from the Calm Belt...!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the preparations are finished. \NWait a little while.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Smells good!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... This is the real deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.44,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man, how long do we have to wait?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.46,0:12:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe about 4-5 hours...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.03,0:12:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bokuden-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.29,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,why is the Navy after Apis? \NDo you have any idea?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Apis! Do you have any idea?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You said there was a reason \Nbut you didn't want to tell.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh that! I lied.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then none at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,None at all?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.89,0:12:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, there's nothing on this island. \NNothing but an old legend.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.61,0:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Legend?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.60,0:13:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The residents of this island are said \Nto be descendants of Lost Island people
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.23,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,who prospered but sank into the sea \Ntens of thousands of years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.45,0:13:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,On Lost Island, there lived \Ndragons called Millennial Dragons.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.49,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The bones of those dragons \Nare called Dragonite...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it's said to be an elixir of immortality.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But a legend like that is no reason \Nfor the Navy to get involved.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.96,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Why is the Navy doing \Nthis in the first place?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing I don't get.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.46,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this legend hold some \Nsort of clue or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, the first king
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.68,0:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,– of Lost Island was Iscardunk.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,– Here we go again...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.93,0:13:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, King PokePortes had three children.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The oldest son was BokeHontas, \Nthe second son was BokeBonboko, and
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,– the third son was BokeBokepon.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,– Shhh!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.74,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, the king said to these three,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.28,0:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Listen. Go find the tree that grows stars, \Nwhich is said to be in dragon's valley.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So BokeHontas, BokeBonboko and BokeBokepon
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.83,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,journeyed out, one to the sea,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,– Once Grandpa starts that story,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.54,0:14:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,– one to the mountain and one to the forest.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,– it'll take forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,– I'm not gonna listen to all that.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.59,0:14:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now, the 317th King IngriMongri III's son
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey, how long is this gonna go on?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,– IngriGrimori was quite a wise ruler.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.33,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,– Who knows.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.14,0:14:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He had 18 children. His 18 children...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...He was a king who
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.98,0:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,carried out major reforms.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.85,0:14:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,– This King Ikemenes had so many children.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,– Ahhh, I'm starving...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,– We won't be able to eat
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,– until this story is over, will we?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}– We won't be able to eat the pork buns until then?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.48,0:14:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,– He had many princes. 65 of them!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,– Pork buns?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,– I hear it was like, "If you throw a stone,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.31,0:14:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,– Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,– it'll hit one of the princes."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,– I gotta take a leak.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pork buns...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Grandpa Ryu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming this way! \NWhat am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Don't come here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pork buns smell yummy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.90,0:15:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hit him yet, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh, pork buns...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.79,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And, the 1,111th... no,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.58,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the 1,121st King was HokeHontas.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, NemeNememitas
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey, where're you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.13,0:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,– thought about what he could do
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,– I'm worried about Luffy
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,– since he's gone for a long time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,– to protect this kingdom.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,– So I'll go check.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,– Then, he made preparation
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,– That's not fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,– Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s lovely even when she sneaks out.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,– before large countries attacked them.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! Good grief!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.82,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! Not even one bun is left!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is yummy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.49,0:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy?! How do you intend to make \Nup for eating everyone's share?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.66,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What made this trail?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Dead end?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.55,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.72,0:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.43,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A hole.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they went across here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.34,0:16:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspension Bridge...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the other side of the mountain.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How far did they go?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.66,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.82,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was fine. \NThese weird pirates saved me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're not that scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.96,0:17:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry. \NI brought Grandpa Bokuden's pork buns.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. No! Slow down!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.59,0:17:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. I still don't know yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.63,0:17:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm searching very hard, \NI still haven't found a clue yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who on earth Apis is talking to.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.81,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Apis! Who're you talking to?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just jump out and say "hey"!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.94,0:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't come here!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.32,0:18:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.08,0:18:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,– Amazing! Amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,– Stop it! I said stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.55,0:18:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.47,0:18:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real thing! Is he alive?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.10,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Leave him alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe... that it really exists...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought that dragons were just legends!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.64,0:18:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible! \NWhere did you come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.03,0:18:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You want to go home, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.04,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu says that you \Ncan be his friend, Luffy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he can tell you're a good person.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.84,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, how could you read Grandpa Ryu's mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.01,0:19:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow did.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow...?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How did {\i1}you{\i0} know?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be... a devil fruit...?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the power of a devil fruit, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.74,0:19:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I ate one called \NWhisper-Whisper Fruit or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.61,0:19:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I've become \Nable to read animals' minds.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you knew a wind was coming that time.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. The seabirds told me that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.62,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Grandpa Ryu thanks to \Nthe Whisper-Whisper Fruit, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.77,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard such a sad voice before...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.08,0:20:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I'm coming to help you now!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.80,0:20:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you who called me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He had lost his energy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he got separated \Nfrom his friends and
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.01,0:20:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that since then he had \Nbeen looking for Lost Island,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,where the dragons' nest is.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.49,0:20:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Lost Island sink a long long time ago?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.86,0:20:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu says that the \Nisland will surface again.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.36,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it's about time,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.28,0:20:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but he no longer clearly remembers where it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.15,0:20:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotten very old and lost the energy to fly.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.04,0:20:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But he keeps telling me \Nthat he wants to go back.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.38,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna help, but I can't figure out \Nwhere such an island exists at all...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The legend by itself doesn't really give me a clue...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.97,0:21:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I asked the Navy who happened \Nto stop by this island about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.31,0:21:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a mistake. \NThey were looking for Dragonite.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragonite... you mean the one for immortality?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.65,0:21:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They took you away because of such a thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.82,0:21:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They told me to tell them \Neverything I knew and took me away.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The pendant that I made with a claw
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.49,0:21:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu gave me may have been another reason, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you escaped in that storm...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,– You are too reckless! \N– I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.45,0:21:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I keep this a secret to \Nthe villagers and even to Bokuden-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.25,0:21:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to cause troubles for them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.17,0:21:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to take Grandpa Ryu back \Nto his home no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.38,0:21:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He always tells me that he'll \Nget his energy back for sure
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,once he goes back to the dragons' nest.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.34,0:21:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find it for him no matter \Nhow many years it takes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.82,0:21:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure... No matter what it takes, I'll find it for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.06,0:22:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then! I'll take him there!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.15,0:22:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Were you listening?! \NLost Island sank into the sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.78,0:22:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But since the legendary \NMillennial Dragon actually exists,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Lost Island also exists somewhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.54,0:22:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,An island that's not even on a map?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.09,0:22:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's why we're going!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.79,0:22:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,An island that's not even on a map, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.63,0:22:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what the heck? Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.29,0:22:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.38,0:22:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.63,0:22:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.13,0:22:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.13,0:22:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that that's been decided, eat more!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.26,0:22:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Luffy, I forgot to tell you...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.35,0:22:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Ryu is a little senile.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.56,0:22:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl had a pendant with \Na Millennial Dragon's claw.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She must know about Lost Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.78,0:22:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That darn girl who knows the secret of the Dragonite...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.74,0:22:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely capture her this time!
